                <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Peking</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1911-09-15">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 15, 1911</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The Cabinet has proposed Yuan Shih Kai for Canton Viceroy and the proposal is
                    having serious consideration.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Williams.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
